<subSubSection type="nomenclature">
<paragraph>
[[ 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
Cordylancistrus 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Isbrücker">Isbruecker</normalizedToken>
</taxonomicName>
]]
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="30">
The genus 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Isbrücker">Isbruecker</normalizedToken>
(1980) with 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="torbesensis">C. torbesensis (Schultz, 1944)</taxonomicName>
as the type and only species. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Isbrücker">Isbruecker</normalizedToken>
(1980: 48) stated that: “ 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
seems related to the genus 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Lasiancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Lasiancistrus</taxonomicName>
, from which it can easily be distinguished by its exceptionally wide head”. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Pérez">Perez</normalizedToken>
and Provenzano (1996) described 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:1ED84969-F7D9-407A-864E-2DB1BF71CA99" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus perijae Pérez &amp; Provenzano R. 1996" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="perijae">C. perijae</taxonomicName>
, indicated some external characters that define the genus 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
and postulated a close relationship between 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
and the genus 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:16C36868-333C-4936-8EBD-D7FF5DB1E003" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Chaetostoma" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Chaetostoma Tschudi 1846:25" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Chaetostoma</taxonomicName>
. They also presented a biogeographic hypothesis on the distribution of 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="torbesensis">C. torbesensis</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:1ED84969-F7D9-407A-864E-2DB1BF71CA99" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus perijae Pérez &amp; Provenzano R. 1996" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="perijae">C. perijae</taxonomicName>
. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Isbrücker">Isbruecker</normalizedToken>
(2001) included in the genus 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
the species: 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="daguae">C. daguae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:1ED84969-F7D9-407A-864E-2DB1BF71CA99" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus perijae Pérez &amp; Provenzano R. 1996" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="perijae">C. perijae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="platycephalus">C. platycephalus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="platyrhynchus">C. platyrhynchus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="torbesensis">C. torbesensis</taxonomicName>
, without comment. Fisch-Muller (2003) listed the same five species of 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
. Armbruster (2004) indicates that species of the genera 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:16C36868-333C-4936-8EBD-D7FF5DB1E003" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Chaetostoma" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Chaetostoma Tschudi 1846:25" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Chaetostoma</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:315EC98B-E28A-40B6-A248-6F8FB04FFF16" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Leptoancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Leptoancistrus Meek &amp; Hildebrand 1916:254" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Leptoancistrus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:30DD89E4-1A65-4C81-859A-F9F210DB8205" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Dolichancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Dolichancistrus Isbrücker 1980:47" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Dolichancistrus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
together form a monophyletic group, but that 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
is apparently not monophyletic and pointed out that only one basic difference (naked snout) was found between the species of 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:16C36868-333C-4936-8EBD-D7FF5DB1E003" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Chaetostoma" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Chaetostoma Tschudi 1846:25" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Chaetostoma</taxonomicName>
and the species assigned to 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:315EC98B-E28A-40B6-A248-6F8FB04FFF16" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Leptoancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Leptoancistrus Meek &amp; Hildebrand 1916:254" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Leptoancistrus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:30DD89E4-1A65-4C81-859A-F9F210DB8205" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Dolichancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Dolichancistrus Isbrücker 1980:47" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Dolichancistrus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
. He transferred 
<taxonomicName class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="platyrhynchus">Cordylancistrus platyrhynchus</taxonomicName>
to the genus 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:16C36868-333C-4936-8EBD-D7FF5DB1E003" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Chaetostoma" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Chaetostoma Tschudi 1846:25" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Chaetostoma</taxonomicName>
and presented a new diagnosis for 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:16C36868-333C-4936-8EBD-D7FF5DB1E003" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Chaetostoma" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Chaetostoma Tschudi 1846:25" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Chaetostoma</taxonomicName>
while maintaining the rest of the genera. Apparently, the recognition of genera and the assignment of species to a genus are controversial. Transitory, we agree with 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Isbrücker">Isbruecker</normalizedToken>
(2001) and Fisch-Muller (2003) and accept five species in the genus 
<taxonomicName LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:DC189F42-3B10-43C7-9456-96BAED9CB821" class="Actinopterygii" family="Loricariidae" genus="Cordylancistrus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cordylancistrus Isbrücker 1980:48" order="Siluriformes" pageNumber="30" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cordylancistrus</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
